trans-unit.source: Defines an encoder that is used to encode [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)] format images.
trans-unit.target: Definierar en kodare som används för att koda [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)] formatera bilder.

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)] bitmap format supports frame level thumbnails, multiple frames, and frame level metadata.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)] bitmappsformatet stöder nivå miniatyrbilderna, flera ramar och RAM nivån metadata.

trans-unit.source: It does not support global preview, global thumbnails, or global metadata.
trans-unit.target: Det stöder inte globala preview, globala miniatyrer eller globala metadata.

trans-unit.source: Encoding does not work in partial trust.
trans-unit.target: Kodning fungerar inte i partiellt förtroende.

trans-unit.source: See [WPF Partial Trust Security](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for information on partial trust.
trans-unit.target: Se [WPF partiellt förtroende säkerhet](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) information om partiellt förtroende.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffBitmapEncoder"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffBitmapEncoder"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates the type of compression that is used by this [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)] image.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett värde som anger vilken typ av komprimering som används av det här [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)] bild.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption>, and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption> values require that the <xref:System.Windows.Media.PixelFormat> value be set to <xref:System.Windows.Media.PixelFormats.BlackWhite%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption>, och <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption>värden kräver att <xref:System.Windows.Media.PixelFormat>värdet anges till <xref:System.Windows.Media.PixelFormats.BlackWhite%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.PixelFormats.BlackWhite%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Media.PixelFormat> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption>
